properties.Name: CustomerCreditCriteriaRating
properties.Description: This is the Credit Agency period credit rating based upon specific individual Credit Criteria, which are combined to provide an overall credit rating.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: CreditRatingAgencyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Rating Agency.

Columns.Name: CreditCriteriaId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Criteria.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated credit criteria rating is valid.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated credit criteria rating is valid.

Columns.Name: CreditCriteriaRatingId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Criteria Rating.

Columns.Name: MinimumAcceptableCreditCriteriaRating
Columns.Description: The minimum acceptable Credit Criteria Rating for the Customer.

Columns.Name: MaximumAttainableCreditCriteriaRating
Columns.Description: The maximum Credit Criteria Rating attainable by the Customer.

Columns.Name: CreditRatingNote
Columns.Description: Note or comments regarding the Customer period credit rating.
